\id 2TH - Zanaki 2 Thessalonians
\h 2 Abhatesaronike
\toc3 2 Abhatesaronike
\toc2 2 Abhatesaronike
\toc1 Enyaarubha ya kabhiri ya Pauro ku Bhatesaronike
\mt2 Enyaarubha ya kabhiri ya Pauro ku
\mt1 Bhatesaronike
\imt1 Obhutaangiro
\ip Kwiibhaga iguhi kweema Pauro atume enyaarubha yaaye yo okutaanga, akabhona amangʼana kubha, abhiikirirya bha Tesaronike bhatamenyeekereerye bhuzomu ameegyo gaaye agaandi. Abhaandi bhakiiseega kubha Yeesu yaari amariri kukyoora. Na abhaandi bhaari bhatigiri emirimo gyaabhu gyoosi, kwo okubha bhakiisiga kubha, Yeesu yaari arakyoora eriibhaga ryoryoosi. Abhaandi bhateendiri kukora emirimo kwe ekigirirye kyo obhutobhu. Kweego, Pauro akakaama enyaarubha yino ya kabhiri, okubha akyoosye amiiseego kya gayo, gano gataari no obhuheene. Munyaarubha yino ya kabhiri akakumiirirya kubha, Yeesu yaari akyaari kukyoora mukyaaro na akabhakumiirirya okugeenderera kukora emirimo kwo omukya.
\c 1
\s1 Obhukeerya
\p 
\v 1 Enyaarubha yino nikaamiri enye Pauro, hamwe na Sirwano\f + \fr 1:1 \fk Sirwano \ft mukitabhu kya Amahokya ga Abheega arabhirikirwa \fqa Siira.\f* na Timoteo, tubhakaamiiri emwe abhiikirirya na abhahoreeru abhaandi bhoosi, mumwiikiriirye Taatabhugya Taata weetu no Omukuru Yeesu Krisito bhano mukwiikara mumugye gwa Tesaronike.
\p 
\v 2 Orubhaango no omureembe okurwa ku Taata Taatabhugya no Omukuru Yeesu Krisito bhibhe neemwe.
\s1 Abhiikirirya bhatoongerwe ekoro hano bhakunyaaka
\p 
\v 3 Abhahiiri bheetu, ereenderwa tubhuge, “Ozomirye, Taatabhugya,” eriibhaga ryoosi kwiiguru weenyu, kwo okubha obhwiikirirya bhweenyu bhurakura bhukongʼu, kweeki okuseegana kweenyu kurageenderera kukura.
\v 4 Kweego, turiikumya mumakanisa ga Taatabhugya kwe ekigirirye kyo okwiikongʼeererya no obhwiikirirya bhweenyu, munyaako yoosi yino mukubhona.
\p 
\v 5 Gayo goosi gareerekya kubha, obhutini bhwe ekiina kya Taatabhugya ni bhwe eheene. Na kwe ekigirirye kiyo, emwe murabharwa kubha mureenderwa mubhutemi bhwaaye,\f + \fr 1:5 \fk Obhutemi bhwaaye \ft ni hagiro hayo hoosi hano Taatabhugya niwe omukaangati. Rora \ft \it obhutemi bhwa Taatabhugya\it* mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* bhuno mukunyaakira.
\v 6 Taatabhugya arakora ge eheene, ewe arabhaha enyaako bhano bhakubhanyaakya emwe,
\v 7 na arabhaha obhumuunyi emwe bhano mukunyaaka, hamwe neetwe. Arakora gayo hano Omukuru Yeesu araaze okurwa mwiisaaro hamwe na bhamaraika\f + \fr 1:7 \fk Bhamaraika\ft . Rora engʼana \ft \it maraika\it* mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* bhaaye bha amanaga,
\v 8 mumireengeeri gyo omuriro. Yeesu niwe arabhatema bhoosi bhano bhakumwaanga Taatabhugya na bhano bhatakwiigwa Amangʼana Amazomu go Omukuru weetu Yeesu.
\v 9 Obhutemwa bhwaabhu bhurabha bhwo okusikibhwa kirakeego, no okutuurwa kure no Omukuru no obhuguungo bhwaaye obhukuru.
\v 10 Obhutemwa bhuyo bhurabha orusiku rurya Omukuru araaze kuguungibhwa na abhahoreeru\f + \fr 1:10 \fk Abhahoreeru\ft . Rora engʼana yino mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* bhaaye, no okusuungʼaana obhusuuku bhwoosi okurwa kubhoosi bhano bhamwiikiriirye. Neemwe mwoosi murabha gati waabhu, kwo okubha mwiikiriirye amangʼana gano tukabhabhuurira.
\p 
\v 11 Kwe ekigirirye kiyo, turabhasabhira eriibhaga ryoosi, kubha Taatabhugya weetu abhasakirye okwiikara kyeego ekweenderwa mubhubhirikirwa bhweenyu. Kweeki turamusabha kubha, amare amangʼana amazomu goosi gano mukweenda kukora, ne emirimo gyeenyu gyoosi gyo obhwiikirirya.
\v 12 Turasabha ego, okubha eriina ryo Omukuru weetu Yeesu ribhe riraguungibhwa kwe ekigirirye kyeenyu. Kweeki neemwe mubhe muraguungibhwa kwe ekigirirye kyaaye. Gano garatuukana no orubhaango rwa Taatabhugya weetu no Omukuru Yeesu Krisito.
\c 2
\s1 Omukuru Yeesu araaza okubha amusikye omwaangi
\p 
\v 1 Bhoono abhahiiri bheetu, turabhakaamira iguru yo okuuza kwo Omukuru weetu Yeesu Krisito, na kyeego turiikumanie kweewe.\f + \fr 2:1 \xt Rora 1 Abhatesaronike 4:17.\xt*\f* Turabhasabha kubha,
\v 2 mutiitiimaata bhwaangu no okubha ne ehaho orusiku rwo okuuza kwo Omukuru ruhikiri. Hamwe mwiigwiiri ego, okurwa mumangʼana amarebhe go obhurooti, kasi go okurwaaza, kasi enyaarubha yino eriiseegwa kubha erwiiri oweetu.
\v 3 Mutiikirirya muutu wowoosi abhakaangirirye kuryoryoosi rirya, kwo okubha orusiku ruyo rutakuhika, tee eziisiku zirya abhaatu bhaaru bharaamwaange Taatabhugya, hano omwaangi wurya\f + \fr 2:3 \ft Obhugazuro bhwo \fk omwaangi wurya \ft ni mwaangi wa Krisito na wuno akusarya emigiro gya Taatabhugya gyoosi. Omwaangi wuno atari Seetaani, nawe woosi arakora omukoonyo gwo okumwaanga Taatabhugya. Rora engʼana \ft \it Seetaani\it* mu Bhugaruri bhwa Amangʼana Amakongʼu.\f* araarorekane kubhweero. Niwe wuyo araasikibhwe kubhuteero.
\v 4 Ewe araanga ebhigiro bhyoosi bhino abhaatu bhararora kubha ni isaambwa, kasi bhino bhakuseengera, na ariituura iguru ya bhyoosi. Kweeki arasikira no okwiikara mwiiseengerero rya Taatabhugya no okwiikora kubha ewe niwe Taatabhugya.
\p 
\v 5 Mutakuhiita kubha, hano niari hamwe neemwe, nikabhabhuurira gayo goosi?
\v 6 Na mumenyiri kino kikumweerekya bhoono ego, okubha arorekane kwiibhaga rino rikweenderwa.
\v 7 Naabhe bhoono, omwaangi wuyo arakora emirimo eno yiibhisiri. Nawe atakurorekana tee wuno akumurekya okukora emirimo kubhweero araaruusibhweho.
\v 8 Hayo niho omwaangi wuyo araarorekane. Nawe Omukuru Yeesu hano araaze, aramwiita no omwiika okurwa mumunwa gwaaye, na aramusikya kwo obhuguungo bhwo okuuza kweewe.
\p 
\v 9 Eriibhaga ryo okuuza kwaaye, omwaangi wuyo, araaza na amanaga goosi ga Seetaani no okukora ebhyeerekenio ne ebhitiika bhyo orurimi.
\v 10 Arabhakaangirirya kwe eziinzira nzaru, bhoosi bhano bhari munzira yo okubhura, kwo okubha bhatakwiikirirya kuseega obhuheene okubha bhatuuribhwe.
\v 11 Kweego Taatabhugya abhaheeri omweeya bhakaangatwe no obhunagya bhwo okubhabhurya, okubha bhageenderere okwiikirirya orurimi.
\v 12 Hayo, bhoosi bhano bhatakwiikirirya obhuheene, nawe bharazomererwa ebhibhi, bharatinirwa ekiina.
\s1 Okwiimeerera mubhugumiru no okugwaata ameegyo
\p 
\v 13 Nawe etwe, tureenderwa tumubhuurire Taatabhugya, “Ozomirye,” eriibhaga ryoosi kwiiguru weenyu, emwe abhahiiri bheetu bhano museegirwe no Omukuru Yeesu. Tureenderwa kukora ego, kwo okubha Taatabhugya akabhasora emwe okurwa obhweemero bhwo kubhuumbwa, okubha mutuuribhwe. Obhutuuribhwa bhuyo mubhusuungʼaaniri kwe Ekoro Muhoreeru wuno abheerirye, na kwo okwiikirirya obhuheene.
\v 14 Taatabhugya akabhabhirikira, okubha mutuuribhwe kwe enzira ya Amangʼana Amazomu gano twaabharwaaziiri oweenyu. Abhabhirikiiri okubha mubhone okwiisaangya mubhuguungo bhwo Omukuru weetu Yeesu Krisito.
\v 15 Bhoono abhahiiri bheetu, mwiimeerere bhugumiru no okugwaata ameegyo gano mukasuungʼaana, eraabhe ni kwo obhurwaazi bhweetu, kasi kwe eziinyaarubha zyeetu.
\p 
\v 16 Taata weetu Taatabhugya atuseegiri, na kwo orubhaango rwaaye aratugosorerya kirakeego no okutuha eriisigo eriizomu. Turamusabha ewe hamwe no Omukuru weetu Yeesu Krisito kubha,
\v 17 abhagosorerye eziikoro no okubhagumirya, okubha mubhone okugaamba no okukora amangʼana goosi amazomu.
\c 3
\s1 Pauro na abharikyaaye bharasabha amasabhi
\p 
\v 1 Bhoono abhahiiri bheetu, mutusabhire okubha Amangʼana iguru wo Omukuru Yeesu gageenderere kunyaragana bhwaangu, okubha abhaatu bhagasuungʼaane kwo obhusuuku, kyeego gaari kweemwe.
\v 2 Mutusabhire okubha Taatabhugya atutuurye mubhaatu abhabhi na bhe ebhibhi, kwo okubha etari bhoosi bhano bhakwiikirirya amangʼana gayo.
\v 3 Nawe Omukuru Yeesu ni muheene, ewe arabhagumirya emwe no okubhariibha na Seetaani, omubhi wurya.
\v 4 Neewe Omukuru aratuha eriisigo ikuru iguru weenyu, kubha bhoono murakora gano tukabharagania, kweeki mukyageenderera okugakora.
\v 5 Omukuru abhakaangate eziikoro zyeenyu mubhuseegi bhwa Taatabhugya no obhwiikongʼeererya bhuno bhukeerekibhwa na Krisito.
\s1 Obhurekya iguru yo obhutobhu
\p 
\v 6 Abhahiiri bheetu, turabharagania kwe eriina ryo Omukuru Yeesu Krisito kubha, mwiiriihe na abhahiiri bhoosi bhano ni bhatobhu, bhano bhatakugwaata ameegyo gano tukabhaha.
\v 7 Turabhuga ego, kwo okubha emwe mumenyiri kyeego ekweenderwa okweega ekireengyo kyeetu. Hano twaari neemwe, tutaari bhatobhu,
\v 8 kweeki twaari tutakurya ebhyaakurya kumuutu wowoosi bhusa. Nawe twaari turakora emirimo kwo omukya obhutiku no omwiisi, okubha tutamunyaakya muutu wowoosi kweemwe.
\v 9 Tukakora ego, etari kubha tutakweenderwa okubhona ekigiro okurwa kweemwe, nawe tukeenda tubhe ekireengyo kweemwe okubha mutweege.
\v 10 Kweeki hano twaari hamwe neemwe, tukabhaswaagya, “Muutu wowoosi wuno atakweenda okukora emirimo, atarya ebhyaakurya.”
\p 
\v 11 Tubhugiri amangʼana gayo, kwo okubha twiigwiiri bhariho abhaatu abhaandi oweenyu ni bhatobhu, bhatakukora kyokyoosi, nawe bhariisikirya mumangʼana ga abhaandi.
\v 12 Abhaatu bhayo turabharagania no okubhatoongera kubhuturo bhwo Omukuru Yeesu Krisito kubha, bhabhe bharakora emirimo kwo obhusuuku, okubha bhabhone ebhyaakurya bhyaabhu abheene.
\v 13 Nawe emwe abhahiiri bheetu, mutakwa emitwe okukora amazomu.
\p 
\v 14 Kyeego omuutu wowoosi atakweenda okugwaata obhuswaagyo bhweetu, bhuno bhuri munyaarubha yino, mwiiriihe no omuutu wuyo. Mutagwaatana neewe, okubha arore eziisoni.
\v 15 Nawe mutamurora kyo omubhisa, mubhe muramuhiinya kyo omurikyeenyu.
\s1 Amangʼana go okuraga
\p 
\v 16 Bhoono, Omukuru Yeesu omweene, niwe esimuka yo omureembe, abhe arabhaha omureembe eriibhaga ryoosi muziinzira zyoosi. Omukuru abhe hamwe neemwe mwoosi.
\v 17 Enye Pauro nirabhakaamira obhukeerya bhuno kwo okubhoko kwaane omweene. Runo nirwo orukaamo muziinyaarubha zyaane zyoosi, na niigo nikukaama.
\p 
\v 18 Orubhaango rwo Omukuru weetu Yeesu Krisito, rubhe hamwe neemwe mwoosi.
